snippet.title: The Combatribes - Full Arcade Longplay - Technos 1990
snippet.description:
Full gameplay - longplay - walkthrough


The Combatribes (ザ・コンバットライブス?) is a 1990 beat 'em-up game released for the arcades by Technos Japan Corp (the developers of Renegade and Double Dragon). A home version for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System was also released in 1992. The game centers on three vigilantes (identified as cyborgs in the SNES port) who must fight against numerous street gangs in futuristic New York City.
